highlights.text: “Mount Everest” by Labrinth is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 89 spots at #88.
Bad Bunny has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Lo Siento BB:/ (with Bad Bunny & Julieta Venegas)” is the highest at #24.
“Stay Alive (Prod. SUGA of BTS)” by Jung Kook is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #10.
“Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 263 weeks straight.
